Class ServerIdentityRole

java.lang.Object
  java.util.Dictionary
      java.util.Hashtable
          org.productivity.java.habitat4j.common.ServerIdentityRole
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Cloneable, Habitat4JConstants, java.util.Map, java.io.Serializable
public class ServerIdentityRole
extends java.util.Hashtable
implements Habitat4JConstants

This class provides ServerIdentity with one or more roles that can be used later by PropertyListManager to make decisions on which properties to load. A ServerIdentityRole contains information on basic "role" information - database server, application server, web server - as well as other vendor-specific information such as product name, version, and patch level.
